  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>Starlight City is a city where the boundaries of reality blur.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/f92d7a93624c191e86a4769785436a49.poster.avif?t=1737662808\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/f92d7a93624c191e86a4769785436a49.webm?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/f92d7a93624c191e86a4769785436a49.mp4?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Waking up in an unfamiliar place with no memories of the past, you realize you are not alone in your plight. The city's inhabitants also suffer from amnesia, surrounded by mysteries and secrets. Without memories of who you are and where you come from, you meet a scientist. He discovered that someone from deep space is trying to communicate with the townspeople.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/537521cbe1f4ccdb72c3c6c9509df518.poster.avif?t=1737662808\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/537521cbe1f4ccdb72c3c6c9509df518.webm?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/537521cbe1f4ccdb72c3c6c9509df518.mp4?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But to receive the message, a powerful antenna must be assembled. Can you help the scientist find all the necessary parts and uncover the mystery of Starlight City?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What do we have in store for you?</h2><br>🔎 Explore the mysterious city: search every corner of the locations for answers to your questions.<br>👨‍🔬 Help the scientist: gather all the parts for the antenna to receive the mysterious signal from space.<br>🛠️ Crafting: use found resources to create parts and other useful tools.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/a4467cd4cd69b0be126e47723a337016.poster.avif?t=1737662808\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/a4467cd4cd69b0be126e47723a337016.webm?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/a4467cd4cd69b0be126e47723a337016.mp4?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>👽 Maze and battles: overcome the mazes beneath the city, facing enemies or finding ways to avoid them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/dbdcc3a8fff0c347daf599f01488c0c5.poster.avif?t=1737662808\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/dbdcc3a8fff0c347daf599f01488c0c5.webm?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/dbdcc3a8fff0c347daf599f01488c0c5.mp4?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>💬 Interact with characters: talk to the townspeople to learn their stories and get clues.<br>🤨 Quests: Complete interesting tasks that bring you closer to the solution... or not ;)<br>🏭 Build an entire factory to create the necessary parts!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/0024a84fdd0bda8a69ac656f9b5caaa3.poster.avif?t=1737662808\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/0024a84fdd0bda8a69ac656f9b5caaa3.webm?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/0024a84fdd0bda8a69ac656f9b5caaa3.mp4?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🚀 Head to space: collect signals and receive various items for them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/496c5cb39009953cc376593cd75e473f.poster.avif?t=1737662808\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/496c5cb39009953cc376593cd75e473f.webm?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598870/extras/496c5cb39009953cc376593cd75e473f.mp4?t=1737662808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🎧 Atmospheric soundtracks: more than 10 original atmospheric soundtracks written for full immersion in the mysterious city.",
